Vendored files live under src/cgimg/_vendor/ and retain their original behavior.

The VERBATIM subset (image-gen + OAuth core) is synced verbatim from a pinned
upstream commit - see VENDOR_REV for the exact SHA. Re-sync with
scripts/update-vendor.sh (or update-vendor.ps1 on Windows).

A few files are LOCAL adaptations and are NOT overwritten on update:
  - src/cgimg/_vendor/__init__.py                  (package marker; no upstream counterpart)
  - src/cgimg/_vendor/services/account_service.py  (single-account shim replacing the multi-account pool)
  - src/cgimg/_vendor/services/protocol/__init__.py (trimmed to avoid importing un-vendored modules)
  - src/cgimg/_vendor/services/storage/factory.py  (JSON-only storage factory)
